rightwing president augusto pinochet 
announced that hundreds of his critics living in exile may return 
to chile but opponents said the move and others like it are 
aimed only at winning votes in a presidential referendum 
four hours after thursdays announcement isabel allende 44 
the daughter of former president salvador allende flew to 
