<TEXT>
four hostages and heavily armed police 
swat teams spent several tense hours friday waiting out two holdup 
men until the hostages safely made a break for it and police 
discovered the pair had fled 
the hostages spent 3 hours inside a closet believing the holdup 
men were still in the bank then dashed from the building in a bid 
for freedom police said no one was hurt 
