500pound animal that can kill you 
early success came to carlos donate of miami and his guide jay 
medore of clewiston they snagged a 8foot3inch animal only 80 
minutes after they started hunting on lake okeechobee 
once they got the gator reeled up to the side of the boat they 
shot it with a bang stick a firearmlike gadget that is 
allowed under the game commission rules 
we blew one hell of a hole in his head donate said it 
was exciting 
he then taped the gators mouth shut 
its scary putting that tape on his mouth even with a hole in 
his head he said 
